###########################################################################
#  box_shadow_overlap - multiple @ShadowBox arranged so their drop        #
#  shadows visually overlap, exercising z-order and shadow rendering      #
#  in both the PS and SVG back ends.                                      #
###########################################################################

@SysInclude { doc }
@Doc @Text @Begin
@PP
Three shadow boxes packed close enough to overlap their drops:
@DP
@CentredDisplay {
   @ShadowBox { First }
   |-0.6c|
   @ShadowBox { Second }
   |-0.6c|
   @ShadowBox { Third }
}
@DP
Stacked vertically with negative gap (rows overlap shadows):
@DP
@CentredDisplay {
   ^//-0.4c
   @ShadowBox { Alpha shadow }
   /-0.4c
   @ShadowBox { Beta shadow }
   /-0.4c
   @ShadowBox { Gamma shadow }
}
@End @Text
